This service offers a *deterministic* OpenAI-compliant LLM inference endpoint that can be used via multiple clients. A couple of key points:

* By OpenAI compliancy we specifically mean the messages-based Chat Completions API: [https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/chat/create](https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/chat/create),
* By ‚Äúdeterministic‚Äù we specifically mean that one request (prompt, parameters, etc) provided to the API multiple times will produce the **same** output.
  * For eg. setting a different seed but otherwise keeping the request the same will produce a different output.

## curl

```
curl -s -X POST http://192.222.58.254:8001/v1/chat/completions \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "model": "gemma-3-27b-it",
  "max_completion_tokens": 120,
  "seed": 42,
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Write a story about programming"}]
}' | jq
```

### Streaming response

```
curl -s -X POST http://192.222.58.254:8001/v1/chat/completions \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "model": "gemma-3-27b-it",
  "max_completion_tokens": 120,
  "seed": 42,
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Write a story about programming"}]
}'
```

## Vercel AI SDK

[https://ai-sdk.dev/docs/introduction](https://ai-sdk.dev/docs/introduction)

```
import { generateText } from 'ai';
import { createOpenAI } from '@ai-sdk/openai';

const config = {
  baseURL: 'http://192.222.58.254:8001/v1',
  apiKey: 'sk-dummy-custom-key',
  model: 'gemma-3-27b-it'
};

// Create a custom OpenAI client instance
const customOpenAI = createOpenAI({
  baseURL: config.baseURL,
  apiKey: config.apiKey,
});

// Create the model instance using the custom client
const model = customOpenAI(config.model);

async function chatCompletion() {
  console.log('\nüí¨ Testing chat completion...');

  try {
    const result = await generateText({
      model: model,
      messages: [
        { role: 'system', content: 'You are a helpful assistant.' },
        { role: 'user', content: 'What are the benefits of using local AI models?' }
      ],
      seed: 42
    });

    console.log('‚úÖ Chat response:');
    console.log(result.text);
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('‚ùå Error with chat completion:');
    console.error(error.message);
  }
}

// Main execution
async function main() {
  console.log('EigenAI usage via Vercel AI SDK\n');
  console.log('=' + '='.repeat(49));

  console.log(`\nüîß Configuration:`);
  console.log(`   Service: EigenAI`);
  console.log(`   Base URL: ${config.baseURL}`);
  console.log(`   Model: ${config.model}`);
  console.log(`   API Key: ${config.apiKey.substring(0, 10)}...`);

  await chatCompletion();
}

main().catch(console.error);
```
